Here are the instructions to run the program.

Please use the following librarys first:

Jini-core.jar
Jini-ext.jar
Outtrigger.jar
Reggie.jar
Sun-util.jar
Reggie-dl.jar
Mahalo.jar

To run the program in eclipse, in "FP_Main" find the "RunChatProgram.java"

Right click the file and select "Run As" then Run Configuration"

Add a  java application and then in arguments, insert the following into VM Arugments

"-Djava.security.policy=policy.all"

Make sure the policy.all file is added.

Then click apply and then run.